There were 2 other sightings in Winnipeg on or around September 3rd 2013
divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting in the back yard at my girlfriends parents in the hot tub(945-1015pm) looking up at the sky (I always look at the sky late at night in the hot tub) I first noticed a flash of light followed by another flash, I noticed it very well but thought nothing of it, had to of only been a few 100 feet off the ground, I just passed it up as an airplane. Not more then 15 mins later (girl friend had gone inside in the time frame from the first spotting to the second) I saw it again, looked like a star flashing, I kept watching to see if it had a pattern like an airplane strobe. flashed once... twice...three times then it completely disappeared. the pause between flashes was random, not in unison like an airplane flashes were like: Flash........flash...........................flash the time frame in between the second and third flash was long enough to almost make me think it was gone but it flashed that last time and I did not see it again.
